{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/diversion/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Developer's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b9ac0405-d12c-5542-bbc7-4c9f53922285","excerpt":"Meaning Diversion means something that takes attention away from what is happening, or an activity that entertains and relaxes you. It can also refer to a…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#meaning\">Meaning</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\">Grammar and Usage</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#common-meanings\">Common Meanings</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#common-phrases\">Common Phrases</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#collocations\">Collocations</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\">Synonyms or Related</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#antonym\">Antonym</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<h2 id=\"meaning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#meaning\" aria-label=\"meaning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Meaning</h2>\n<p><strong>Diversion</strong> means something that takes attention away from what is happening, or an activity that entertains and relaxes you. It can also refer to a change in route or direction (especially in traffic or military contexts).</p>\n<h2 id=\"grammar-and-usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grammar-and-usage\" aria-label=\"grammar and usage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grammar and Usage</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Part of speech:</strong> Noun</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Countable / Uncountable:</strong> Usually countable</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Typical structures:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>a diversion from something</em> — something that distracts or amuses</li>\n<li><em>traffic diversion</em> — an alternative route due to road closure</li>\n<li><em>create a diversion</em> — to deliberately distract attention</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"common-meanings\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#common-meanings\" aria-label=\"common meanings permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common Meanings</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Distraction or amusement:</strong>\nSomething that diverts your mind or attention.\n<em>Example: Reading novels is a pleasant diversion from work.</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Alternative route:</strong>\nA different way when the normal path is blocked.\n<em>Example: The road was closed, so we took a diversion.</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Tactical distraction:</strong>\nA deliberate action to draw attention away from the main event.\n<em>Example: The soldiers created a diversion to mislead the enemy.</em></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"common-phrases\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#common-phrases\" aria-label=\"common phrases permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common Phrases</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>create a diversion</strong> – to cause a distraction</li>\n<li><strong>traffic diversion</strong> – a route changed due to roadworks</li>\n<li><strong>pleasant diversion</strong> – an enjoyable break or pastime</li>\n<li><strong>minor diversion</strong> – a small detour or distraction</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"collocations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collocations\" aria-label=\"collocations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collocations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>make / create / cause</strong> a diversion</li>\n<li><strong>a welcome / pleasant / brief</strong> diversion</li>\n<li><strong>road / traffic</strong> diversion</li>\n<li><strong>diversion of funds / attention / resources</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>The magician created a diversion to hide his next trick.</li>\n<li>We had to take a long diversion because of the bridge repair.</li>\n<li>For her, painting is a welcome diversion from daily stress.</li>\n<li>The team staged a diversion to allow their allies to escape.</li>\n<li>A book or movie can be a good diversion during tough times.</li>\n<li>There was a diversion on the highway due to a car accident.</li>\n<li>He used humor as a diversion to ease the tense atmosphere.</li>\n<li>The protesters created a diversion while others entered the building.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"synonyms-or-related\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#synonyms-or-related\" aria-label=\"synonyms or related permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Synonyms or Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>distraction</li>\n<li>pastime</li>\n<li>detour</li>\n<li>entertainment</li>\n<li>deviation</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"antonym\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#antonym\" aria-label=\"antonym permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Antonym</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>focus</li>\n<li>concentration</li>\n<li>direct route</li>\n<li>main path</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"diversion meaning and examples","date":"2025-10-26","description":"English learning materials; diversion explanation.","tags":["English","noun"],"featuredImage":{"publicURL":"/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/diversion.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8e8b8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/b5658/diversion.png","srcSet":"/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/acb7c/diversion.png 256w,\n/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/ccc41/diversion.png 512w,\n/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/b5658/diversion.png 1024w","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/22bfc/diversion.webp 256w,\n/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/d689f/diversion.webp 512w,\n/static/9b0646d65b1026768da8a45e4682e90d/67ded/diversion.webp 1024w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"}]},"width":1024,"height":1024}}}}},"relatedPosts":{"nodes":[]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/crevice/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"crevice meaning and examples"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fraud/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"fraud meaning and examples"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b9ac0405-d12c-5542-bbc7-4c9f53922285","previousPostId":"e4f8fbeb-24f9-5e3e-9b8e-4bf12a1e5617","nextPostId":"03ebcabb-c2b7-579d-995d-7ddb298666f6","relatedPosts":[]}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}